Clone this repo to the desktop, do not install any other packages in this directory

Install ROS Melodic on your Jetson

Create a new folder on the desktop named "Robot Workspace"

Create catkin workspace in "Robot Workspace" by comleting ROS setup tutorial: "Installing and configuring your ROS environment"

Enter your catkin_ws directory

Clone the zed_ros_wrapper into the src directory ( https://github.com/stereolabs/zed-ros-wrapper )

Install PyTorch using the following commands:
	$ pip3 install torch torchvision
	$ pip3 install -r requirements.txt

Create a new branch for all cloned repos and name it for your robot



Clone the specified branches

